<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.2">
<l>poruntā varakkar veñcamattup poṉṟa vaṉṟu puḷḷūrntu</l>
<l>peruntōḷ māli talaipuraḷap pērnta varakkar teṉṉilaṅkai</l>
<l>yiruntār tammai yuṭaṉkoṇṭaṅ keḻilār pilattup pukkoḷippa</l>
<l>karuntāḷ cilaikaik koṇṭāṉūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram, the city of the one who had in hand</l>
<l rend="indent">a bow with strong tips,</l>
<l>Riding a bird once so that enemy demons perished in heated battle,</l>
<l>So the head of great-armed Māli rolled,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] so that the demons who had fled gathering together</l>
<l>With those who were in Lankā of the South, entering an underworld</l>
<l rend="indent">filled with beauty, were hidden there.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
